# Back in Singapore

[Krombacher Pils
Non-Alcoholic](https://www.lazada.sg/products/krombacher-pils-non-alcoholic-i303278244-s536556990.html)
is 23.80SGD for 6x330ml. ~12SGD per litre, which is only a couple of dollars
cheaper than the variety with alcohol!

A case of [Paulaner Weissbier
Alcohol-Free](https://www.lazada.sg/products/paulaner-weissbier-alcohol-free-case-i301158835-s527244539.html)
at 61.20SGD seems like the best deal. ~6SGD per litre! Or 3SGD for a big 500ml
bottle.

The Paulaner tastes great to me after exercise. Loving it. Hopefully it doesn't make me fat.

